{"id": "1417503289964232784", "channel_id": "1417503289964232784", "type": 0, "author_id": "1166632516136996886", "author_name": "morimensstaff02", "author_bot": false, "content": "守密人你好：\n       弥萨格大学校务处将于 <t:1758030000:F> 进行校内设施修复，更新完成后您将得到通知，重新进入游戏。对于更新可能给大家带来的不便，我们会准备一份补给物资以示歉意。祝大家调查顺利！ \n  \n【补给物资】\n在线维护补偿：银芯*50\n  \n【领取条件】\n领取时间截至2025年9月30日23:59。请记得及时前往邮箱领取补给物资哦。  \n \n【更新内容】\n一、问题修复\n● 修复了唤醒体「塔薇」的技能「四翼渐生」的力量偷取效果未生效的问题。\n● 修复了「档案馆」遗漏「黑阳垂照的永夏」活动场景的问题。\n● 修复了第七章「欲河」中的错别字。\n● 由于V2.3.2.3更新中发生的意外错误，9月15日、9月16日的「幻梦深潜」或者「相位对弈」排行榜无法进行正常结算。\n    ○ 对于在这两日内完成过相应玩法登上排行榜、或使用「代理凭证」的守密人，我们将在72小时内，按照「幻梦主宰」的头衔，为您补发对应日期的排行奖励。\n    ○ 部分守密人已经获取了较低档位的结算奖励。对于这部分守密人，我们将为您补发对应的奖励差额，使奖励总额与「幻梦主宰」头衔的奖励标准相当。\n \n二、英文本地化\n● 修复了钥令「脑中之音」、命轮「女王的戒律」，唤醒体「莱克」、「雷娅」的天赋「灵塑适性」描述，唤醒体「菲茵特」、「塔薇」、「凯蒂古拉」部分技能描述错误地变回了机器翻译的问题。\n● 优化了敌人「杜勒赛因」的战斗中台词与机制提示。\n● 优化了部分界面的文本翻译，修复措辞一致性：命轮叠位，剧情关卡共鸣点位，融灾黑潮界面。\n● 优化了死亡抵抗、吞噬、反击的词条介绍可读性。", "timestamp": "2025-09-16T13:32:00.265000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-16T13:34:47.613000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1417503290207506573", "filename": "lQDPJwvYGmhlHTPNAyDNBLCwUuNpTh4piMEFWSaXsTLvAA_1200_800.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 131426, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1417503289964232784/1417503290207506573/lQDPJwvYGmhlHTPNAyDNBLCwUuNpTh4piMEFWSaXsTLvAA_1200_800.jpg?ex=69cc7590&is=69cb2410&hm=375e65c8eb3a7a8e4bf77580b407bb32f396879070586de9295d622687ff0746&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1417503289964232784", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.3.2.4 在线维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
{"id": "1417503371958419558", "channel_id": "1417503289964232784", "type": 0, "author_id": "1166632516136996886", "author_name": "morimensstaff02", "author_bot": false, "content": "**V2.3.2.4 Online Maintenance Announcement**\n\nDear Keeper,\nThe Mythag Administration Office will conduct campus facility maintenance on  <t:1758030000:F>. You will be notified once the update is complete and you can re-enter the game. As an apology for any inconvenience caused by the update, we will provide a supply package. Wishing everyone a successful investigation!\n \n[Compensation]\nOnline Maintenance Compensation: Silver*50\n \n[Claim Conditions]\nThe claiming time ends on September 30, 2025 at 23:59. Please remember to go to your mailbox in time to claim the supply materials.\n \n[Update Content]\n1. Problem Fix\n● Fixed the issue where the strength stealing effect of the Awakener \"Tawil\" skill \"Four Wings\" was not functioning.\n● Fixed the issue where the \"Archive\" missed the event scene of \"Eternal Summer under the Black Sun.\"\n● Fixed typos in Chapter 7 \"River of Desire\".\n● Due to an unexpected error in the V2.3.2.3 update, the \"Phantasmal Dive\" or \"Traphase\" rankings for September 15th and September 16th cannot be settled normally.\n    ○ For Keepers who have completed the corresponding gameplay and made it onto the leaderboard, or used the \"Proxy Certificate\" within these two days, we will resend the ranking rewards for the corresponding dates within 72 hours, based on the title of \"Dominion.\"\n    ○ Some Keepers have already received lower tier settlement rewards. For this group of Keepers, we will compensate you with the corresponding reward difference to make the total rewards equivalent to the standards of the \"Dream Dominion\" title.", "timestamp": "2025-09-16T13:32:19.814000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-16T13:34:55.414000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1417503289964232784", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.3.2.4 在线维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
{"id": "1417503409694572607", "channel_id": "1417503289964232784", "type": 0, "author_id": "1166632516136996886", "author_name": "morimensstaff02", "author_bot": false, "content": "2. English Localization\n●  Fixed the descriptions of the Posse \"Voice in the Head,\" Wheel of Destiny \"Queen's Edict,\" and Awakeners Ryker and Leigh's Soulforge Aptitude. Also resolved the issue where some skill descriptions of the Awakeners Faint, Tawil, and Kathigu-Ra incorrectly reverted to machine translation.\n● Optimized the enemy Doresain's battle lines and mechanism hints.\n● Optimized the text translation of some UI interfaces and fixed wording consistency: Wheel of Destiny Ascension, Story Stage Resonance Points, D-Tide Interface.\n● Improved the readability of the descriptions for Death Resistance, Devour, and Counter.", "timestamp": "2025-09-16T13:32:28.811000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1417503289964232784", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.3.2.4 在线维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
